{"tid":1377172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇見好多前線發夢被捕","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:08:11.000Z","uid":164603,"like":120,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ab30eb89dfa185669a4c54f6c23b2f65f77b0f79","tid":1377172,"uid":164603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"然後開始有班尋晚有份叫勇武走嘅人開post <br />\n覺得點解自己勸完前線be water 反而被算賬話唔應該鼓吹人走<br />\n好啦 而家前線死守被圍捕 我地失去好多前線 心有不甘<br />\n<br />\n但請大家宣洩完就算了<br />\n其他前線睇已經少左手足 睇完post只會覺得更灰<br />\n大家坐埋同一條船 我地必需緊守<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割蓆不譴責不篤灰</span><br />\n<br />\n希望今日事件完左之後 大家可以focus返賽後檢討<br />\n唔好散播太多負面情緒<br />\n香港人 加油"},{"pid":"6b04dd877e28ec6fafa1417e68ced50793b270c3","tid":1377172,"uid":164603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"be4725368ae501baa475b9d41a5b219a17e15ee5","tid":1377172,"uid":81449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:12:22.000Z","msg":"同感 幫推"},{"pid":"c1f18f94a3b8f2f3e50790495bec92eedca4ba96","tid":1377172,"uid":54721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"衰係衰係戰術問題<br />\n唔係單純走定留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a24b2f2a0044839047cd8be72048031cc75562c","tid":1377172,"uid":94484,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"最主要係對住速龍突擊冇方法<br />\n次次一衝就散變落單"},{"pid":"9a53b6d45eb74a153e9dd8d953f3f2c9975ffde0","tid":1377172,"uid":164603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be4725368ae501baa475b9d41a5b219a17e15ee5","tid":1377172,"uid":81449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:12:22.000Z","msg":"同感 幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"thx ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都唔係好願意係呢個時勢睇到呢類discouraging嘅言論"},{"pid":"1a3f0fbf2a0ed1210a08f65dd464d2ad773d14b0","tid":1377172,"uid"